OL,7,FBristol Bears star Abbie Ward has said
OL,8,Fshe hopes to change perceptions about
OL,9,Fpregnancy in women's sport after she
OL,10,Freturned to rugby just 17 weeks after
OL,11,Fgiving birth.
OL,13,FThe 30-year-old gave birth to Hallie
OL,14,Fearlier this year but was able to make
OL,15,Fa winning return to the Bristol Bears
OL,16,Fteam in the club's match against Sale
OL,17,Fat Ashton Gate.
